          <div class="space-y-1 pb-3 pt-2">
            <a href="/solutions/opsfolio/#why-opsfolio" class="block border-l-4 border-transparent py-2 pl-3 pr-4 text-white hover:border-red-400 hover:bg-gray-50 hover:text-gray-800">Why Stature?</a>
